An email processed by {{MailItemStore.createMailItemChunk}} needs the memory of about 3-4 times the size of the message, typically in contiguous chunks.

This is a semi-frequent cause of OOMEs in JIRA Cloud.  ~30MB seems to be about the cut off before things start to fail.

